{"data":[{"date":"05:18 01/08","title":"HLV U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng h\u1ebft lo ng\u1ea1i sau 2 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0110N\u00c1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/7/22/hlv-u16-viet-nam-van-khong-het-lo-ngai-sau-2-thang-loi-lien-tiep-o-giai-dna.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0110T U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Campuchia \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 31/7, \u0110T U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Timor Leste v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eadm 4-0.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng h\u1ebft lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng h\u1ebft lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/7/22/hlv-u19-viet-nam-noi-gi-khi-lam-doc-co-cau-bai-tai-giai-u19-quoc-te.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm nh\u01b0ng U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng do k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Indonesia v\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u00f4ng V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t ch\u01b0a y\u00ean t\u00e2m v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t: &ldquo;Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i d\u00f9 r\u1eb1ng h\u00f4m nay c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, v\u1eabn c\u00f2n b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. L\u1ebd ra ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u01a1n. D\u1eabu sao t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p Indonesia \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, HLV tr\u01b0\u01a1ngr U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam cho bi\u1ebft:&nbsp;&ldquo;Tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chia \u0111\u1ec1u 50-50 cho c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00eam l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 11 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i d\u00e8 ch\u1eebng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ebft ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u00e2u d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U16 Indonesia s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 2/8 t\u1edbi.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-u16-viet-nam-40-u16-dong-timor-u16-dong-nam-a-2018-325-192404.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/video-tong-hop-u16-viet-nam-40-u16-dong-timor-u16-dong-nam-a-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-u16-viet-nam-40-u16-dong-timor-u16-dong-nam-a-2018-325-192404.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 4-0 U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Timor (U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018)</span><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 U16 Campuchia 1-0, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 g\u1eb7p U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Timor...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4907","checkdouble":"192435"},{"date":"05:43 01/08","title":"CLB Juventus ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tuy\u1ec3n sinh t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/clb-juventus-chinh-thuc-tuyen-sinh-tai-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tuy\u1ec3n sinh t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong th\u00e1ng 8 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>CLB Juventus tuy\u1ec3n sinh t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CLB Juventus tuy\u1ec3n sinh t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CLB Juventus tuy\u1ec3n sinh t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/37889006_411314022726153_7336238775078486016_n.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n Juventus b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u tuy\u1ec3n sinh t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00e0y 31-7 v\u1eeba qua, h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Juventus Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch tuy\u1ec3n sinh\u00a0kh\u00f3a \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Theo \u0111\u00f3, CLB l\u1eebng danh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh l\u1eadp v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 01/11/1897 t\u1ea1i Italia s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u00ed t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1eeb B\u1eafc v\u00e0o Nam t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 10 t\u1edbi 19/8.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd l\u00e0 s\u1ebd x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea1i t\u1ec9nh B\u00e0 R\u1ecba - V\u0169ng T\u00e0u theo m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. H\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n Juventus Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o ra c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a CLB Juventus t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u00ed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ecdn, ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u0103m lo v\u1ec1 sinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, h\u1ecdc v\u0103n h\u00f3a, ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef v\u00e0 trang b\u1ecb c\u00e1c k\u0129 n\u0103ng s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft trong th\u1eddi gian tuy\u1ec3n sinh, CLB Juventus c\u1eed HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng H\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Juventus to\u00e0n c\u1ea7u \u2013 \u00f4ng Gianluca Settanni qua v\u00e0 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ecdn l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Ngo\u00e0i s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Gianluca Settanni, \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 HLV n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham gia tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ecdn g\u1ed3m: HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1ed3ng S\u01a1n, HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh,\u2026<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ecbch tuy\u1ec3n sinh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n Juventus s\u1ebd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng: B\u00e0 R\u1ecba - V\u0169ng T\u00e0u (10-8), TP HCM (10 \u0111\u1ebfn 11-8), C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 (13-8), \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng (15-8), H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i (16 \u0111\u1ebfn 17-8), H\u00e0 T\u0129nh (19-8). \u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tuy\u1ec3n sinh c\u1ee7a CLB n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u00ed c\u00f3 n\u0103m sinh t\u1eeb 2006 \u2013 2009. C\u00e1c th\u00ed sinh c\u00f3 nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng tham gia d\u1ef1 thi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u0103ng k\u00ed qua s\u1ed1 hotline 0903 864 486, ho\u1eb7c fanpage Juventus Academy Vietnam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: robotoslab-regular, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4906","checkdouble":"192436"},{"date":"06:02 01/08","title":"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00f3n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tin x\u1ea5u v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/dt-olympic-viet-nam-don-them-mot-tin-xau-ve-nhan-su.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Nguy\u1ec5n Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng may g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018.</h2><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7&nbsp;Nguy\u1ec5n Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nguyen Trong Dai dinh chan thuong\" title=\"Nguy\u1ec5n Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/dt-olympic-viet-nam-don-them-mot-tin-xau-ve-nhan-su.png\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u00e1t ng\u00e0y Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o thi \u0111\u1ea5u</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u qua 31/7, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a PVF. Sau nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng, HLV Park Hang Seo chia Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u00e0nh 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 t\u1eadp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng may cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ngay \u0111\u1ea7u bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng may m\u1eafn khi b\u1ecb l\u1eadt c\u1ed5 ch\u00e2n&nbsp;\u1edf t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec nguy hi\u1ec3m. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, HLV Park Hang Seo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u b\u00e1c s\u0129 Choi - b\u00e1c s\u0129 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1eebng \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb cho Tu\u1ea5n Anh \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Viettel r\u1eddi s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i ki\u1ec3m tra ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c BHL U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o trong nay mai. Tuy nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf v\u1edbi HLV Park Hang Seo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ki\u1ec3u n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 kho\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb 1 \u0111\u1ebfn 2 tu\u1ea7n m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. C\u00f2n nh\u1edb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng b\u1ecb t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 SLNA \u0111\u00e3 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t kho\u1ea3ng 1 th\u00e1ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4905","checkdouble":"192437"},{"date":"06:17 01/08","title":"H\u1ed3ng Duy n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi m\u1ea5t su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 ASIAD?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/1/hong-duy-noi-gi-sau-khi-mat-suat-du-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Phong H\u1ed3ng Duy \u0111\u00e3 ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i chia tay \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi m\u1ea5t su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 ASIAD?</h2><h2>H\u1ed3ng Duy ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u00ec m\u1ea5t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 ASIAD</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Phong H\u1ed3ng Duy n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi m\u1ea5t su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Phong H\u1ed3ng Duy n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi m\u1ea5t su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Noi-kho-\u201cthu\u201d-va-\u201cdot\u201d-deu-phai-keu.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u1ed3ng Duy l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi ASIAD 2018 v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ed3ng Duy l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau khi anh g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, v\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y c\u1ea7n 1 th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Phong H\u1ed3ng Duy cho hay: \"T\u00f4i bu\u1ed3n v\u00e0 kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo g\u1ecdi l\u00ean U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 ASIAD 2018 n\u00e0y m\u00ecnh ng\u1ed3i nh\u00e0\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00f4i d\u00ednh ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c r\u1ea5t h\u1ee5t h\u1eabng. T\u00f4i mong v\u00e0 ch\u00fac th\u1ea7y Park Hang Seo v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u1edf bu\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3m tra th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c chi\u1ec1u 28/07, sau m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c, H\u1ed3ng Duy \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00f9i \u1edf nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. G\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n ngay sau \u0111\u00f3, H\u1ed3ng Duy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn t\u1ebf ki\u1ec3m tra v\u00e0 k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u00ecnh Ph\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ecb c\u0103ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u00f9i sau ch\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i. Ca ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y kh\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-don-them-mot-tin-xau-ve-nhan-su-168-192437.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/dt-olympic-viet-nam-don-them-mot-tin-xau-ve-nhan-su.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-don-them-mot-tin-xau-ve-nhan-su-168-192437.html\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00f3n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tin x\u1ea5u v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1</span><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Nguy\u1ec5n Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng may g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:#222222;mso-fareast-language:ko\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4904","checkdouble":"192438"},{"date":"03:00 01/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP MU vs Real Madrid 07h00 ng\u00e0y 1/8 (ICC 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/mu-vs-real-madrid-tran-dau-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp MU vs Real Madrid: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Real Madrid vs MU gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup ICC 2018 l\u00fac 07h00 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 1/8.</h2>(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nDANH S\u00c1CH XU\u1ea4T PH\u00c1T<br>\r\nMANCHESTER UNITED (4-4-1-1)</strong>: David de Gea; Matteo Darmian, Eric Bailly, Timothy Fosu-Mensah, Luke Shaw; Fred, Ander Herrera, Scott McTominay, Andreas Pereira; Juan Mata, Alexis Sanchez.<br>\r\n<strong>REAL MADRID (4-2-3-1)</strong>: Kiko Casilla; Alvaro Odriozola, Jesus Vallejo, Javier Sanchez, Theo Hernandez; Marcos Llorente, Federico Valverde; Vinicius, Gareth Bale, Daniel Ceballos; Karim Benzema.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>TH\u00d4NG TIN</h2>\r\nM.U thua 12, ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 7/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t theo k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1. <br>\r\n12/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a M.U c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 2 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1edbi rung. <br>\r\nReal Madrid th\u1eafng 9, thua 10/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t theo k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1. <br>\r\n17/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Real Madrid c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1edbi rung. <br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp MU vs Real Madrid tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ICC 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 18 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp MU vs Real Madrid tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ICC 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 18 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/nhan-dinh-mu-vs-real-madrid-07h05-ngay-18-icc-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">MU vs Real Madrid</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM.U v\u1eafng t\u1edbi&hellip; 17 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7<br>\r\nTheo k\u00eanh ESPN, t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 M.U v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Real Madrid v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 \u0111i ngh\u1ec9 World Cup 2018 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi&hellip; 17 ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Ander Herrera, Chris Smalling, Eric Bailly l\u00e0 3 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. Herrera d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eaft c\u00e1 ch\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Liverpool. C\u00f2n Bailly d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Milan. Bailly \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1ecbn \u0111au thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Liverpool v\u00ec Smalling ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00fac kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng. <br>\r\n<h2>PH\u00c1T BI\u1ec2U</h2>\r\nHLV Julen Lopetegui (Real): &ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. M.U l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh. Mourinho c\u0169ng l\u00e0 HLV t\u00e0i n\u0103ng. \u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi h\u1ecd lu\u00f4n mang l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c r\u1ea5t h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n&rdquo;. <br>\r\nHLV Jose Mourinho (M.U): &ldquo;M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. M.U kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T</h2>\r\nT\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1 b\u00e0n hi\u1ec7p 1<br>\r\n13/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a M.U c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1edbi rung \u1edf hi\u1ec7p 1. 16/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Real Madrid c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. NHM n\u00ean \u0111\u1ee3i sau 15 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng hi\u1ec7p 1. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>MU 1-4 Liverpool (ICC 2018) </strong>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/29/Man-Utd-vs-Liverpool.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4903","checkdouble":"192425"},{"date":"04:00 01/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Tottenham vs AC Milan 07h30 ng\u00e0y 1/8 (ICC 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/tottenham-vs-ac-milan-07h30-ngay-18-tran-dau-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Tottenham vs AC Milan: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Tottenham vs AC Milan gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup ICC 2018 l\u00fac 07h30 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 1/8.</h2>(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<h2>TH\u00d4NG TIN XUNG QUANH</h2>\r\n- Tottenham thua 9, th\u1eafng 1/10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y theo k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br>\r\n- Milan th\u1eafng 7, thua 3/10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y theo k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br>\r\n- Tottenham th\u1eafng 4, thua 6/10 tr\u1eadn xa nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y theo k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br>\r\n- Milan th\u1eafng 7, thua 3/10 tr\u1eadn xa nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y theo k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br>\r\n- Tottenham th\u1eafng 2, thua 1/3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y v\u1edbi Milan theo k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Tottenham vs AC Milan 07h30 ng\u00e0y 18 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Tottenham vs AC Milan 07h30 ng\u00e0y 18 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/nhan-dinh-tottenham-vs-ac-milan-07h30-ngay-18-icc-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Tottenham vs AC Milan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T</h2>\r\nT\u1eeb 3 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean<br>\r\nC\u00f3 t\u1edbi 13/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Tottenham k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb 3 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean. Hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u0169ng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong 4/7 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Milan. R\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 quy lu\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u1ebd l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTottenham 4-1 Roma (ICC 2018)\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/26/Tottenham-4-1-Roma.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4902","checkdouble":"192426"},{"date":"05:00 01/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Barca vs Roma 09h00 ng\u00e0y 1/8 (ICC 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/barca-vs-roma-tran-dau-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Barca vs Roma: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Barcelona vs Roma gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup ICC 2018 l\u00fac 09h00 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 1/8.</h2>(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<h2>TH\u00d4NG TIN</h2>\r\nRoma th\u1eafng k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u1edf 5/7 l\u1ea7n 2 \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p nhau tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\nBarca kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u1edf 5/7 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y (thua 4, h\u00f2a 1), c\u00f2n Roma kh\u00f4ng thua k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u1edf 6/8 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua (th\u1eafng 4, h\u00f2a 2).<br>\r\n5/6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 4/6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Roma \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 l\u1ebb.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Barca vs Roma tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ICC 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 18 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Barca vs Roma tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ICC 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 18 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/nhan-dinh-barca-vs-roma-09h05-ngay-18-icc-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca vs Roma</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T</h2>\r\nN\u1ed5 t\u00e0i hi\u1ec7p 1<br>\r\n3/5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong hi\u1ec7p 1. 8/9 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Barca c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1edbi rung trong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd n\u1ed5 t\u00e0i hi\u1ec7p 1.<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/29/Highlight-Barca-vs-Tottenham.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4901","checkdouble":"192427"},{"date":"18:06 31/07","title":"4 l\u00fd do tin r\u1eb1ng Los Blancos s\u1ebd s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/4-ly-do-tin-rang-los-blancos-se-sup-do-o-mua-giai-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t \u1edf th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111ang trong th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao v\u1edbi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u, tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do Real Madrid s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp theo.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean \u1edf CLB Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Perez &ndash; s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng lu\u00f4n \u1edf m\u1ee9c cao ng\u1ea5t. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e0ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh t\u1edbi 14 danh hi\u1ec7u t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng trong 5 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 3 danh hi\u1ec7u Champions League li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, v\u00e0 4 l\u1ea7n trong 5 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 m\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i cho nh\u1eefng HLV m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn, \u0111\u01a1n c\u1eed nh\u01b0 Julen Lopetegui. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia n\u00e0y v\u1eeba m\u1edbi mang n\u1ed7i nh\u1ee5c \u1edf World Cup 2018, khi \u0111i \u0111\u00eam v\u1edbi CLB v\u00e0 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 ng\u00e0y l\u00e0 di\u1ec5n ra. V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t HLV c\u00f3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, vi\u1ec7c qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi Real Madrid, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7. V\u1edbi B\u1ed1 gi\u00e0 Perez, \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n nghe b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 l\u00fd do n\u00e0o cho nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. Nh\u01b0ng li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng n\u00e0o l\u1edbn h\u01a1n 3 chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap C1 trong 3 n\u0103m li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp?<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 l\u00fd do tin r\u1eb1ng Los Blancos s\u1ebd s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"4 l\u00fd do tin r\u1eb1ng Los Blancos s\u1ebd s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/27/4-ly-do-tin-rang-Los-Blancos-se-sup-do-o-mua-giai-toi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real Madrid kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng l\u00e0m n\u00ean chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nV\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Lopetegui</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n n\u1eefa c\u0169ng li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng. Lopetegui \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha, v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng tham gia m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn n\u00e0o (b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup). Th\u1eddi c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u, \u00f4ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf Real Madrid v\u00e0 Barcelona.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">So s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Zidane l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3. HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1ed1n l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t quan tr\u1ecdng b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t trong th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 Galacticos \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. V\u00e0 cho d\u00f9 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0i v\u1edf chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Zidane kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV (\u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 Real ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n), \u00f4ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh l\u1edbn, v\u00e0 l\u00e0 Galacticos &ndash; bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a CLB, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lopetegui th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean s\u1ebd c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y vinh d\u1ef1 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i, v\u00e0 HLV s\u1ebd ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng. <strong>L\u00fac n\u00e0y, Lopetegui mong m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb s\u1ec9 nh\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 may, sau nh\u1eefng tai ti\u1ebfng m\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y ra.</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 l\u00fd do tin r\u1eb1ng Los Blancos s\u1ebd s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Lopetegui s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Real Madrid s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/lope.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>V\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Lopetegui d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nL\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Real \u0111ang l\u00e3o h\u00f3a<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ea7u h\u1ebft nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec1u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ee9ng ngo\u00e0i c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, v\u00ec h\u1ecd x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed9 khung qu\u00e1 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2014 t\u1edbi gi\u1edd, Los Blancos m\u1edbi \u0111em v\u1ec1 1 bom t\u1ea5n l\u00e0 James Rodriguez &ndash; c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm b\u1eadt b\u00e3i t\u1eeb m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 v\u1eeba qua, Luka Modric v\u1eabn l\u00e0 linh h\u1ed3n tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng, nh\u01b0ng anh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ch\u1ea1m m\u1ed1c 33 tu\u1ed5i. Nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Real c\u0169ng gi\u00e0 theo th\u1eddi gian, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Sergio Ramos (32), Keylor Navas (31), Karim Benzema (30) v\u00e0 Gareth Bale (29).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i b\u1edfi n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua, nh\u01b0ng m\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf x\u1ee9ng t\u1ea7m cho d\u00e0n h\u1ea3o th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu v\u1eabn \u0111ang tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh cao v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng l\u00e0m n\u00ean nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac h\u1ecd chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb xu\u1ed1ng d\u1ed1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 l\u00fd do tin r\u1eb1ng Los Blancos s\u1ebd s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng con ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho Real \u0111\u1ec1u b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tu\u1ed5i b\u0103m\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eefng con ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho Real \u0111\u1ec1u b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tu\u1ed5i b\u0103m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a CR7</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 s\u1ef1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c n\u00e0o v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 1, d\u00f9 c\u00f3 \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i, 100 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u00e0 Real nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i, v\u1eabn l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 thi \u0111\u1ec3 CLB n\u00e0y \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t si\u00eau ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng 50 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng/m\u00f9a.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 l\u00fd do tin r\u1eb1ng Los Blancos s\u1ebd s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a Ronaldo v\u1edbi Juventus r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111ong \u0111\u1ebfm.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/HLV-Julen-Lopetegui-phat-bieu-ve-Gareth-Bale-day-tu-tin-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>CR7 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf 1vs1 v\u1edbi Ronaldo, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 n\u01b0\u1edbc Real \u0111em Leo Messi v\u1ec1. B\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng, h\u1ecd \u00edt nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 2 ng\u00f4i sao v\u1edbi 2 vai tr\u00f2 kh\u00e1c nhau &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3ng vai ng\u00f2i n\u1ed5 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i. Ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd \u0111em v\u1ec1 Lewandowski v\u00e0 Hazard m\u1ed9t l\u00fac, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd \u1ed5n th\u1ecfa, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng Real s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nguy.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ea5t \u0111i bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a CLB, l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111ang tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e0 l\u00e3o h\u00f3a, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o CLB v\u00e0 v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng, \u0111\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do Real Madrid s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-real-madrid-4-cai-ten-huong-loi-nhat-duoi-thoi-lopetegui-180-191534.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/goc-real-madrid-4-cai-ten-huong-loi-nhat-duoi-thoi-lopetegui.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-real-madrid-4-cai-ten-huong-loi-nhat-duoi-thoi-lopetegui-180-191534.html\">G\u00f3c Real Madrid: 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Lopetegui</span><br>\r\nSau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Zidane, Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng. v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1edf Real Madrid c\u1ee7a HLV...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/cristiano-ronaldo-roi-real-madrid-khep-lai-18-nam-ky-nguyen-bong-vang-180-192169.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/28/cristiano-ronaldo-roi-real-madrid-khep-lai-18-nam-ky-nguyen-bong-vang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/cristiano-ronaldo-roi-real-madrid-khep-lai-18-nam-ky-nguyen-bong-vang-180-192169.html\">Cristiano Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real Madrid: Kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i 18 n\u0103m k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng</span><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Cristiano Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real Madrid khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u00e0ng gia l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 18 n\u0103m kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng n\u00e0o trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4900","checkdouble":"192418"},{"date":"22:17 31/07","title":"C\u00f3 hay kh\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c Real chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Willian?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/23/co-hay-khong-viec-real-chi-70-trieu-bang-mua-willian.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid mua Willian l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Daily Mail c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Willian</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111\u00e3 3 l\u1ea7n h\u1ecfi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 50, 53 v\u00e0 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Willian bu\u1ed9c Barca ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Malcom.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n Real Madrid mua Willian v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n Real Madrid mua Willian v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/Khong-co-chuyen-Real-Madrid-mua-Willian-voi-gia-70-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real mu\u1ed1n chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Willian</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM.U c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Willian, song Chelsea kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp th\u00eam s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh cho M.U, h\u1ecd ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Willian, theo Don Balon Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988, \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00fang b\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Chelsea mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. HLV Lopetegui r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb mua Willian t\u1eeb Real</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid mua Willian l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Daily Mail \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. T\u1edd b\u00e1o c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng ch\u01b0a h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willian la cai ten choi noi bat trong hiep mot tran Chelsea vs West Ham.\" title=\"Willian l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs West Ham.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/Chi-toi-70-trieu-bang-MU-quyet-tam-mua-Willian-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb mua Willian t\u1eeb Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb mua Willian n\u00e0o t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Real, n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecd c\u0169ng s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i. HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Willian v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/willian-chinh-thuc-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-mu-va-real-madrid-172-192368.html\" target=\"_blank\">Willian ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</span>, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London. Th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch cho NHM The Blues v\u00e0 HLV Sarri.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Willian, Chelsea c\u00f2n \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Courtois v\u00e0 Hazard, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Real Madrid.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4899","checkdouble":"192421"},{"date":"22:45 31/07","title":"Barca ch\u1edd th\u00eam 7 ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi sao PSG","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/3/28/Tien-ve-Adrien-Rabiot-muon-toi-Anh-trong-tuong-lai-gan-hinh-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot t\u1eeb PSG, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1edd th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Rabiot</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAndres Iniesta \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n thi \u0111\u1ea5u, Paulinho c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Trung qu\u1ed1c. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Arthur, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn HLV Ernesto Valverde c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot t\u1eeb PSG \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot t\u1eeb PSG \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/27/Barca-muon-mua-Adrien-Rabiot-tu-PSG-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0</h3>\r\n            <h3>Rabiot l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBarca v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi, Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi PSG \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2019, anh mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i thay v\u00ec ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Tuchel.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAdrien Rabiot \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi PSG, anh quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i, h\u1ecd kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Rabiot \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay c\u1ea3 khi m\u1ea5t tr\u1eafng Adrien Rabiot \u1edf H\u00e8 2019, PSG c\u0169ng quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ra \u0111i. HLV Tuchel \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca ch\u1edd th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Rabiot</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot t\u1eeb PSG, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1edd th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Rabiot\" title=\"tien ve Rabiot\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/Vuot-mat-Arsenal,-Barca-muon-mua-Steven-Nzonzi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca ch\u1edd th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu Rabiot</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong 7 ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1eb7p tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp BL\u0110 PSG \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i. Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 n\u1ed5i lo\u1ea1n\u00a0\u0111\u1ec3 ra \u0111i b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi Rabiot c\u00f4ng khai ra \u0111i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a TBN s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c bu\u1ed9c PSG ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 La Liga ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, n\u1ebfu Rabiot kh\u00f4ng quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i, Barca s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/barca-nham-muc-tieu-so-1-cua-arsenal-thay-rabiot-180-192175.html\" target=\"_blank\">Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Nzonzi c\u1ee7a Sevilla</span>, ng\u00f4i sao 30 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4898","checkdouble":"192423"},{"date":"23:02 31/07","title":"T\u1eeb b\u1ecf Hazard, Real chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Dortmund","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/9/tu-bo-hazard-real-chi-70-trieu-euro-mua-sao-khung-dortmund.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Christian Pulisic, Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1ef9 thay v\u00ec chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn mua Eden Hazard.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1ee5 Eden Hazard</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nEden Hazard r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Real Madrid, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Chelsea c\u0169ng b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge sau 6 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Christian Pulisic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Christian Pulisic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/28/Real-Madrid-muon-mua-Christian-Pulisic-voi-gia-70-trieu-euro-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>S\u1ef1 c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn c\u1ee7a Chelsea khi\u1ebfn Real g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1ee5 Hazard\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nReal bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Hazard \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Chelsea c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef Hazard \u1edf l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Hazard, song Chelsea \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. N\u1ebfu Los Blancos chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Neymar \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Don Balon, Real quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng chi 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Hazard, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c thay v\u00ec \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Pulisic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Christian Pulisic, Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1ef9 thay v\u00ec chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn mua Eden Hazard.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Christian Pulisic\" title=\"Christian Pulisic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/Chelsea-muon-mua-Christian-Pulisic-voi-gia-65-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real mu\u1ed1n chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euri mua Christian Pulisic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Pulisic l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Dortmund. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1ef9 r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh, \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng hay ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m. HLV Lopetegui \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDortmund bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 70 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1998. \u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Ruhr nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 70 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Don Balon, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Pulisic h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Real Madrid. Ng\u00f4i sao 19 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha n\u1ebfu K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4897","checkdouble":"192424"},{"date":"00:40 01/08","title":"Barca chi 11 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1edd t\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/10/16/barca-chi-11-trieu-bang-mua-cai-ten-khong-the-ngo-toi-cua-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca s\u1ebd mua Simon Mignolet c\u1ee7a Liverpool trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Jasper Cillessen ra \u0111i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Sky Sports \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cillessen c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1eeb khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jasper Cillessen kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf s\u00e2n Camp Nou. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Marc-Andre ter Stegen khi\u1ebfnc\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jasper Cillessen\" title=\"Jasper Cillessen\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/7/Chelsea-quan-tam-toi-thu-mon-Jasper-Cillessen--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jasper Cillessen c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a t\u1edbi, t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Barca, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca, hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jasper Cillessen, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid. Napoli c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan. C\u1ea3 Chelsea v\u00e0 Napoli \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca mua Mignolet thay Cillessen</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan Ra \u0111i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a TBN s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf. Barca s\u1ebd mua Simon Mignolet c\u1ee7a Liverpool trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Jasper Cillessen ra \u0111i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Sky Sports \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 11 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Mignolet\" title=\"thu mon Mignolet\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/20/barca-bat-ngo-muon-ky-hop-dong-voi-hang-thai-cua-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Mignolet</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/klopp-up-mo-kha-nang-tram-karius-va-mignolet-172-192217.html\" target=\"_blank\">Klopp c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Mignolet </span>c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Theo \u0111\u00f3, s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Alisson khi\u1ebfn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi b\u1ecb h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Mignolet kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n r\u1eddi Liverpool. N\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Barca, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu t\u1edbi Camp Nou, Mignolet s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, anh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Marc-Andre ter Stegen. Ngo\u00e0i Barca th\u00ec Besiktas c\u1ee7a Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4896","checkdouble":"192432"},{"date":"23:59 31/07","title":"Klopp: \"Kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Coutinho\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/klopp-khong-ai-co-the-thay-the-duoc-vi-tri-cua-coutinho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Philippe Coutinho, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u1edf Anfield.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Coutinho r\u1eddi Liverpool t\u1edbi Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Philippe Coutinho. \u1ede H\u00e8 2017 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb song v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Liverpool nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m nay \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"coutinho liverpool\" title=\"coutinho liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/4/3/dani-alves-khuyen-barca-mua-cau-thu-xuat-sac-nhat-cua-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Coutinho c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 160 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m nay</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 160 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb Barca khi\u1ebfn Liverpool kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u1ea1i, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e0nh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Camp Nou.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 m\u1ea5t Coutinho v\u00e0o tay Barca song Liverpool v\u1eabn thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, h\u1ecd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o Top 4 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 thua Real Madrid 1-3 trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft\u00a0Champions League 2017/18.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThe Kop \u0111ang s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Virgil van Dijk, Fabinho, Naby Keita, Xherdan Shaqiri v\u00e0 Alisson. S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u00fap kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Man City l\u00e0 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, HLV Klopp \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu trong tay m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Coutinho</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Philippe Coutinho, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u1edf Anfield.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Philippe Coutinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Philippe Coutinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/klopp-khong-ai-co-the-thay-the-duoc-vi-tri-cua-coutinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jurgen Klopp kh\u0103ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Coutinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u00e1o ch\u00ed n\u00f3i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c Liverpool mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thay th\u1ebf Coutinho. T\u00f4i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. C\u1eadu l\u00e0 Coutinho.\u00a0C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t. Coutinho c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh, \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung\u00a0t\u00e2m\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cM\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c nhau, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi Coutinho \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t, l\u00e0 duy nh\u1ea5t, v\u00ec v\u1eady \u0111\u1eebng h\u1ecfi t\u00f4i khi n\u00e0o s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4895","checkdouble":"192429"}]}